{"tid":823700,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益，理性討論］交通警告系統","createTime":"2018-09-17T00:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T05:09:01.000Z","uid":192104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb5b3ee53bee1c5e95802d805a7866b8a7162a6d","tid":823700,"uid":192104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:30:34.000Z","msg":"山竹過後，大量冧樹，車路不通，巴士停洗，地鐵塞人。但以現時風勢，雨勢都好難怪天文台。但指意公司放打工仔假就實在係太天真了。<br />\n<br />\n如果以現時交通情況，去計算一個交通流暢指標，分黃紅黑三等，黑色就唔洗番工，有冇得諗？<br />\n<br />\n除左風暴後，呢個指標亦可以cover 現時未有既指標，例如地震，火山（當然香港冇呢d,舉個例姐）<br />\n<br />\n咁當然條formula 要calibrate到唔會出現好多黑色既情況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪傻啦，快d番工啦"},{"pid":"abddf31985250642b9579f011a24d28e0996c8e9","tid":823700,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:31:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a7fe305811d177d352b6cd87448efdb3f9bb3c6","tid":823700,"uid":192104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T00:35:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06a207645dc073a767f794e944c1a6e23b913289","tid":823700,"uid":192104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e32433b5e47f664f97d1087f17d78089e2f1f5","tid":823700,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"諗法新穎，但交通情況一時時，又點𨤳定？"},{"pid":"5b4b91676d415694067d48e9e4fbe3d99bd160ce","tid":823700,"uid":192104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6e32433b5e47f664f97d1087f17d78089e2f1f5","tid":823700,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"諗法新穎，但交通情況一時時，又點𨤳定？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"可以叫巴士公司，地鐵公司提供通車資料<br />\n路政署提供路面塞車資料<br />\n<br />\n實際公式當然要睇過去數據去定"},{"pid":"a15e5261fd30c51da32ebd5c1de109690